{
  "id": "2021-11-18_screen_english",
  "date": "2021-11-18",
  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "I am haunted by a single_ obsessive thought",
  "movie": "",
  "duration_sec": 746.35,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2021-11-18_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 13.52,
      "text": "English"
    },
    {
      "start": 13.52,
      "end": 34.3,
      "text": "자막 없이 영화를 볼 수 있는 그날까지"
    },
    {
      "start": 34.3,
      "end": 35.9,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.9,
      "end": 38.4,
      "text": "11월에 함께하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 38.4,
      "end": 39.6,
      "text": "아넷 반닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 39.6,
      "end": 41.12,
      "text": "서샤 로넌"
    },
    {
      "start": 41.12,
      "end": 43.28,
      "text": "빌리 하울 주연의"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.28,
      "end": 44.82,
      "text": "다시골 갈매기"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.82,
      "end": 45.57,
      "text": "워우"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.57,
      "end": 46.49,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.49,
      "end": 47.49,
      "text": "헬로"
    },
    {
      "start": 47.49,
      "end": 49.23,
      "text": "top of the morning to you and everyone"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.23,
      "end": 49.93,
      "text": "GMP"
    },
    {
      "start": 49.93,
      "end": 50.93,
      "text": "굿모닝"
    },
    {
      "start": 50.93,
      "end": 52.77,
      "text": "아니 제가 주중해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 52.77,
      "end": 53.61,
      "text": "during the week"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.61,
      "end": 55.29,
      "text": "되게 재미있었던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.29,
      "end": 56.25,
      "text": "특히 혼자 있을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 56.25,
      "end": 57.79,
      "text": "I've said the director's name"
    },
    {
      "start": 57.79,
      "end": 58.71,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 58.71,
      "end": 60.53,
      "text": "over and over again"
    },
    {
      "start": 60.53,
      "end": 61.71,
      "text": "You've said his name"
    },
    {
      "start": 61.71,
      "end": 63.89,
      "text": "이런 경험은 또 처음이에요"
    },
    {
      "start": 63.89,
      "end": 64.65,
      "text": "Mr. Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 64.65,
      "end": 65.89,
      "text": "계속 생각이 나더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 65.89,
      "end": 67.79,
      "text": "He's an amazing playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 67.79,
      "end": 69.43,
      "text": "legendary Russian playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 69.43,
      "end": 70.39,
      "text": "그래서인가"
    },
    {
      "start": 70.39,
      "end": 71.63,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 71.63,
      "end": 72.67,
      "text": "Anton Chekhov"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.67,
      "end": 75.19,
      "text": "이렇게 반복적으로 연습을 했던 기억이 납니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 75.19,
      "end": 76.07,
      "text": "It's a sexy name"
    },
    {
      "start": 76.07,
      "end": 77.39,
      "text": "그래서인가"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.39,
      "end": 77.83,
      "text": "Anton"
    },
    {
      "start": 77.83,
      "end": 78.39,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.39,
      "end": 81.15,
      "text": "And he was both a doctor and a writer"
    },
    {
      "start": 81.15,
      "end": 82.19,
      "text": "He was"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.19,
      "end": 82.83,
      "text": "Wow"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.83,
      "end": 83.15,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.15,
      "end": 85.65,
      "text": "He grew up from not a very wealthy family"
    },
    {
      "start": 85.65,
      "end": 86.97,
      "text": "His grandfather"
    },
    {
      "start": 86.97,
      "end": 88.31,
      "text": "paternal grandfather"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.31,
      "end": 89.43,
      "text": "Chinnareboji"
    },
    {
      "start": 89.43,
      "end": 90.69,
      "text": "was a serf"
    },
    {
      "start": 90.69,
      "end": 92.65,
      "text": "which is almost like a slave"
    },
    {
      "start": 92.65,
      "end": 93.71,
      "text": "back in Russia"
    },
    {
      "start": 93.71,
      "end": 95.37,
      "text": "similar to a slave"
    },
    {
      "start": 95.37,
      "end": 97.05,
      "text": "so from a very poor background"
    },
    {
      "start": 97.05,
      "end": 98.69,
      "text": "but he studied medicine"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.69,
      "end": 100.43,
      "text": "and he became a doctor"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.43,
      "end": 100.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 100.95,
      "end": 102.83,
      "text": "and also he loved writing"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.83,
      "end": 104.85,
      "text": "so he started writing short stories"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.85,
      "end": 106.51,
      "text": "and then plays"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.51,
      "end": 108.73,
      "text": "and he kept up his doctor life"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.73,
      "end": 109.91,
      "text": "to support his family"
    },
    {
      "start": 109.91,
      "end": 111.47,
      "text": "because he had a wife and kids"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.47,
      "end": 112.89,
      "text": "and he needed to pay the bills"
    },
    {
      "start": 112.89,
      "end": 114.71,
      "text": "so he kept on working"
    },
    {
      "start": 114.71,
      "end": 116.09,
      "text": "even though he got really sick"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.09,
      "end": 116.85,
      "text": "at one time"
    },
    {
      "start": 116.85,
      "end": 118.31,
      "text": "he caught tuberculosis"
    },
    {
      "start": 118.31,
      "end": 120.47,
      "text": "so he got deathly sick"
    },
    {
      "start": 120.47,
      "end": 121.85,
      "text": "but he just kept on working"
    },
    {
      "start": 121.85,
      "end": 123.51,
      "text": "and didn't even get it treated"
    },
    {
      "start": 123.51,
      "end": 128.37,
      "text": "굉장히 근면성실한 성격의 소유자였던 것 같습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.37,
      "end": 129.59,
      "text": "A hardworking man"
    },
    {
      "start": 129.59,
      "end": 131.37,
      "text": "And he succeeded eventually"
    },
    {
      "start": 131.37,
      "end": 132.63,
      "text": "as a playwright"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.63,
      "end": 133.71,
      "text": "너무 다행입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 133.71,
      "end": 136.73,
      "text": "And he also left many words"
    },
    {
      "start": 136.73,
      "end": 140.11,
      "text": "되게 흥미로운 어록들을 많이 남겼더라고요"
    },
    {
      "start": 140.11,
      "end": 142.69,
      "text": "And among them, this one was so funny"
    },
    {
      "start": 142.69,
      "end": 143.45,
      "text": "A funny one"
    },
    {
      "start": 143.45,
      "end": 144.63,
      "text": "Yeah, 제가 소개를 해드릴게요"
    },
    {
      "start": 144.63,
      "end": 148.25,
      "text": "If you are afraid of loneliness, don't marry"
    },
    {
      "start": 148.25,
      "end": 149.73,
      "text": "Don't marry?"
    },
    {
      "start": 149.79,
      "end": 150.99,
      "text": "Yeah, what do you think about this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 152.19,
      "end": 154.63,
      "text": "Well, let me speak carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.63,
      "end": 155.81,
      "text": "Very carefully"
    },
    {
      "start": 155.81,
      "end": 157.47,
      "text": "네, 외로움이 두렵다면"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.47,
      "end": 158.85,
      "text": "결혼하지 마라"
    },
    {
      "start": 158.85,
      "end": 160.67,
      "text": "라는 어록을 남겼다고 합니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 160.67,
      "end": 163.61,
      "text": "If you are lonely, get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 163.61,
      "end": 165.19,
      "text": "이 얘기가 아니었단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.19,
      "end": 167.91,
      "text": "Yeah, I would think that would be the thing to say"
    },
    {
      "start": 167.91,
      "end": 169.53,
      "text": "If you are alone, get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 169.53,
      "end": 172.51,
      "text": "But yeah, I've been a married man myself"
    },
    {
      "start": 172.51,
      "end": 175.45,
      "text": "with only females, women in the house"
    },
    {
      "start": 175.45,
      "end": 177.03,
      "text": "I do understand this"
    },
    {
      "start": 177.03,
      "end": 178.75,
      "text": "I do feel lonely sometimes"
    },
    {
      "start": 178.75,
      "end": 179.53,
      "text": "아, 그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 179.53,
      "end": 182.11,
      "text": "사실 we shouldn't rely too much on people"
    },
    {
      "start": 182.11,
      "end": 184.17,
      "text": "Yeah, you can't rely on people"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.17,
      "end": 184.55,
      "text": "그럼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 184.55,
      "end": 185.55,
      "text": "Even your own family"
    },
    {
      "start": 185.55,
      "end": 187.75,
      "text": "믿을 사람이 없는 건가요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.47,
      "end": 189.95,
      "text": "아무튼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.95,
      "end": 191.69,
      "text": "But still, marriage is better than being alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 191.69,
      "end": 192.31,
      "text": "Yeah, sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 192.31,
      "end": 194.37,
      "text": "You'll be even more lonely in the end"
    },
    {
      "start": 194.37,
      "end": 195.19,
      "text": "if you just stay alone"
    },
    {
      "start": 195.19,
      "end": 196.33,
      "text": "In my opinion"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.33,
      "end": 197.91,
      "text": "So I support marriage"
    },
    {
      "start": 197.91,
      "end": 198.89,
      "text": "Get married"
    },
    {
      "start": 198.89,
      "end": 200.49,
      "text": "Do it like me"
    },
    {
      "start": 200.49,
      "end": 204.07,
      "text": "네, 결혼 장녀 이야기를 들으셨습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 204.07,
      "end": 205.77,
      "text": "다 똑같이 해야 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.77,
      "end": 207.15,
      "text": "전만 하면 안 돼요"
    },
    {
      "start": 207.15,
      "end": 208.35,
      "text": "다 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.35,
      "end": 208.79,
      "text": "다 같이"
    },
    {
      "start": 208.79,
      "end": 209.19,
      "text": "하자"
    },
    {
      "start": 209.19,
      "end": 210.55,
      "text": "아, 오케이, 좋습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 210.55,
      "end": 212.41,
      "text": "오늘 장면 듣고 오겠습니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 212.41,
      "end": 213.81,
      "text": "How do I begin?"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.07,
      "end": 214.85,
      "text": "Day and night"
    },
    {
      "start": 214.85,
      "end": 216.59,
      "text": "I am haunted"
    },
    {
      "start": 216.59,
      "end": 219.91,
      "text": "by a single obsessive thought"
    },
    {
      "start": 219.91,
      "end": 221.41,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 221.41,
      "end": 222.23,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 222.23,
      "end": 223.13,
      "text": "I must write"
    },
    {
      "start": 223.13,
      "end": 225.53,
      "text": "No sooner do I finish one story"
    },
    {
      "start": 225.53,
      "end": 227.53,
      "text": "than for God knows what reason"
    },
    {
      "start": 227.53,
      "end": 228.39,
      "text": "I have to write another"
    },
    {
      "start": 228.39,
      "end": 229.55,
      "text": "and another"
    },
    {
      "start": 229.55,
      "end": 230.23,
      "text": "and another"
    },
    {
      "start": 230.23,
      "end": 232.79,
      "text": "What's so beautiful and brilliant about that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 232.89,
      "end": 233.95,
      "text": "It's a ridiculous life"
    },
    {
      "start": 233.95,
      "end": 235.3,
      "text": "Here I am"
    },
    {
      "start": 235.3,
      "end": 236.62,
      "text": "I'm talking to you"
    },
    {
      "start": 236.62,
      "end": 238.44,
      "text": "I'm getting all riled up"
    },
    {
      "start": 238.54,
      "end": 240.29,
      "text": "네, 오늘은"
    },
    {
      "start": 240.29,
      "end": 243.41,
      "text": "Boris의 목소리를 쭉 들어보셨는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 243.41,
      "end": 245.55,
      "text": "Do you think he was happy enough?"
    },
    {
      "start": 245.55,
      "end": 247.19,
      "text": "He doesn't sound very happy"
    },
    {
      "start": 247.19,
      "end": 248.83,
      "text": "He seems kind of anxious"
    },
    {
      "start": 248.83,
      "end": 250.33,
      "text": "and nervous"
    },
    {
      "start": 250.33,
      "end": 252.37,
      "text": "He's really obsessed"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.37,
      "end": 254.23,
      "text": "He needs to write"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.23,
      "end": 255.25,
      "text": "He needs to write all the time"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.25,
      "end": 255.63,
      "text": "맞아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 255.63,
      "end": 258.39,
      "text": "이제 막상 좋아하던 게"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.39,
      "end": 259.55,
      "text": "일이 되잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.55,
      "end": 259.89,
      "text": "그러면"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.89,
      "end": 262.55,
      "text": "마냥 행복하기만 한 것은 아니죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 262.55,
      "end": 263.03,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 263.03,
      "end": 264.55,
      "text": "If you watch him in the movie"
    },
    {
      "start": 264.55,
      "end": 266.65,
      "text": "He's always looking at nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.65,
      "end": 266.67,
      "text": "He's always looking at nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 266.67,
      "end": 268.07,
      "text": "or looking around him"
    },
    {
      "start": 268.07,
      "end": 270.51,
      "text": "not just to enjoy the nature"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.51,
      "end": 271.75,
      "text": "but for his work"
    },
    {
      "start": 271.75,
      "end": 272.23,
      "text": "Right"
    },
    {
      "start": 272.23,
      "end": 273.09,
      "text": "He takes notes"
    },
    {
      "start": 273.09,
      "end": 274.53,
      "text": "Oh, there's a cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 274.53,
      "end": 275.77,
      "text": "It's a pretty cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 275.77,
      "end": 277.21,
      "text": "I'm going to write about this cloud"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.21,
      "end": 279.11,
      "text": "So he has like"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.11,
      "end": 279.71,
      "text": "강박"
    },
    {
      "start": 279.71,
      "end": 280.97,
      "text": "강박이 진짜 심해요"
    },
    {
      "start": 280.97,
      "end": 281.69,
      "text": "그렇죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 281.69,
      "end": 282.89,
      "text": "저 같은 경우를"
    },
    {
      "start": 282.89,
      "end": 284.81,
      "text": "한번 감정이입을 해봤어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 284.81,
      "end": 285.69,
      "text": "저도 이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 285.69,
      "end": 287.21,
      "text": "영어를 좋아해가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 287.21,
      "end": 288.93,
      "text": "그래도 감사하게도"
    },
    {
      "start": 288.93,
      "end": 289.61,
      "text": "이 일을"
    },
    {
      "start": 289.61,
      "end": 290.73,
      "text": "직업을 삼아가지고"
    },
    {
      "start": 290.73,
      "end": 291.77,
      "text": "살고 있지 않습니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.77,
      "end": 295.01,
      "text": "I just try to enjoy the pain"
    },
    {
      "start": 295.01,
      "end": 296.37,
      "text": "Enjoy the pain?"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.09,
      "end": 297.69,
      "text": "Ironically"
    },
    {
      "start": 297.69,
      "end": 299.41,
      "text": "That's an oxymoron"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.41,
      "end": 299.69,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 299.69,
      "end": 301.69,
      "text": "Sometimes it's really painful"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.69,
      "end": 303.33,
      "text": "and hard to stand"
    },
    {
      "start": 303.33,
      "end": 305.79,
      "text": "가끔은 저도 힘들 때가 있어요"
    },
    {
      "start": 305.79,
      "end": 306.19,
      "text": "Sure"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.19,
      "end": 306.95,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 306.95,
      "end": 308.59,
      "text": "There's a famous saying"
    },
    {
      "start": 308.59,
      "end": 309.87,
      "text": "No pain, no gain"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.87,
      "end": 310.33,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
